## Under the following terms:

### Attribution

You must give appropriate credit, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made. You may do so in any reasonable manner, but not in any way that suggests the licensor endorses you or your use.

**Required Attribution Format:**
```
Powered by LyraFrame (https://github.com/petehsu/LyraFrame)
Licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0
```

### NonCommercial

You may NOT use the material for commercial purposes. Commercial purposes include but are not limited to:

- Selling the software or any derivative works
- Using the software in a commercial product or service
- Using the software to generate revenue directly or indirectly
- Offering the software as a paid service (SaaS)
- Including the software in a product that is sold

### No Selling

You may NOT sell this software or any derivative works under any circumstances without explicit written permission from the copyright holder.

### No Charging

You may NOT charge users any fee for access to or use of this software or any derivative works.

