## Commercial Licensing

If you wish to use LyraFrame for commercial purposes, you MUST:

1. **Contact the Author** — Reach out to obtain a commercial license before any commercial use
2. **Maintain Attribution** — Even with a commercial license, you must maintain proper attribution
3. **Negotiate Terms** — Commercial licensing terms will be negotiated on a case-by-case basis

**Contact for Commercial Licensing:**
